.TH "fsl_rio_config_read" 9 "fsl_rio_config_read" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
fsl_rio_config_read \- Generate a MPC85xx read maintenance transaction
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" fsl_rio_config_read
.BI "(struct rio_mport *mport "  ","
.BI "int index "  ","
.BI "u16 destid "  ","
.BI "u8 hopcount "  ","
.BI "u32 offset "  ","
.BI "int len "  ","
.BI "u32 *val "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mport" 12
RapidIO master port info
.IP "index" 12
ID of RapdiIO interface
.IP "destid" 12
Destination ID of transaction
.IP "hopcount" 12
Number of hops to target device
.IP "offset" 12
Offset into configuration space
.IP "len" 12
Length (in bytes) of the maintenance transaction
.IP "val" 12
Location to be read into
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Generates a MPC85xx read maintenance transaction. Returns 0 on
success or -EINVAL on failure.
